images.prompt: Perched elegantly on the precipice of a rugged cliff bathed in an ethereal ancient glow, a moon priestess exudes an otherworldly allure in a mesmerizing synthwave aesthetic, her intricate garments blending seamlessly with the night sky while her eyes reflect the deep hues of pewter and petrol green, revealing a deep connection to the celestial energies above; mechanical joints glimmer softly beneath her flowing attire, hinting at the fusion of organic mystique and advanced technology, as the silvery crescent moon looms large behind her, casting an enchanting halo that illuminates the surrounding landscape, creating a captivating contrast of shadows and light that envelops the scene in a dreamlike ambiance, merging the realms of fantasy and reality into a breathtaking tableau of cosmic wonder.
